name: Fever
description: Elevated body temperature above the normal range

name: Fatigue
description: Feeling of tiredness or lack of energy

name: Headache
description: Pain in the head or upper neck

name: Cough
description: Sudden expulsion of air from the lungs

name: Sore Throat
description: Pain or irritation in the throat

name: Runny Nose
description: Excess discharge of fluid from the nose

name: Nausea
description: Feeling of sickness with an inclination to vomit

name: Vomiting
description: Forceful expulsion of stomach contents through the mouth

name: Diarrhea
description: Loose, watery stools occurring more frequently than usual

name: Constipation
description: Difficult or infrequent bowel movements

name: Abdominal Pain
description: Pain felt between the chest and groin

name: Chest Pain
description: Discomfort or pain in the chest area

name: Shortness of Breath
description: Difficulty breathing or feeling breathless

name: Dizziness
description: Feeling faint, woozy, or unsteady

name: Muscle Aches
description: Pain or soreness in muscles

name: Joint Pain
description: Discomfort or pain in joints

name: Skin Rash
description: Visible change in skin color or texture

name: Itching
description: Irritating sensation causing desire to scratch

name: Swelling
description: Enlargement of a part of the body

name: Loss of Appetite
description: Reduced desire to eat

name: Weight Loss
description: Unintentional decrease in body weight

name: Weight Gain
description: Unintentional increase in body weight

name: Blurred Vision
description: Lack of sharpness of vision

name: Confusion
description: Impaired orientation or cognitive function

name: Anxiety
description: Feeling of worry, nervousness, or unease
